name: Cookie don't Clicker | Wowie Jam 3.0 Submission | UNFINISHED
name_original: Cookie don't Clicker | Wowie Jam 3.0 Submission | UNFINISHED
description:
In this clicker game, your goal is to click anything but the cookie!

If you do click the cookie, then prepare for consequences.

= How does this fit the theme? =

In cookie clicker, you progress by clicking right? Well in this game, you progress more failing to click the cookie!
